         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16/2/82 ¶  ¶ It is very kind of you, dear Mr Cheeseman, to send me the fruit of Persoonia Tora. The specimens of drupes will answer my purposes very well. Have you any good fruit-specimens of Sporadan...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.02.16a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Cheeseman</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Auckland Institute and Museum.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">16/2/82</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is very kind of you, dear Mr Cheeseman, to send me the fruit of <name key="Persoonia%20Tora">Persoonia Tora</name>. The specimens of drupes will answer my purposes very well. Have you any good fruit-specimens of <name key="Sporadanthus">Sporadanthus</name> at hand?</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am quite ashamed to tax you &amp; other friends, without doing something in return for you; but really I have had for a long time past not leisure even for my own literary progressive work, as I had to give up a large share of my time for fully 12 months as one of the jurors (in the chemical and 2 other branches) and as one of the general Commissioners for the Exhibition (international).<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>International Exhibition, Melbourne, 1880-1.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have thus not made up any collections of spare specimens for a long time; but as gradually the accumulated &amp; postponed work of my Department is cleared off, I shall also attend to the distribution of spare-specimens of plants, and you shall not be forgotten. The <name key="Poranthera%20alpina">Poranthera alpina</name>, sent by you, is very interesting. In the Australian Alps I saw P. microphylla right up to the snowline, but may have passed P. alpina.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Of course, you receive the volumes of the R.S.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Royal Society.</p>
               </note> of N.S Wales? In the new one I have a systematic index of the 2120 plant-genera, now known as represented in Australia.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B82.13.08.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
